rComments: Great professor, assignments and tests were always fair, and we always knew what topics to study going into them. During this online course, he was also easier with marking, while most profs did the opposite. Very interesting course as well, and he made all the material very clear!

Doing research under Hardens supervisión is not recommended. He seems nice and interested at first but soon forgets about you and your research. Hard to reach him. Took months to get emails back. He is rude and condescending when you try to talk about your research. Not sure what he is like as a prof, just not a good PI! Avoid!
